items.title: Putin Is Playing with Trump
items.description: The master at establishing leverage in negotiations has failed to do so over the president of Russia.

items.title: Gavin Newsom’s Shameless Dodge on the Homeless Crisis
items.description: California’s governor tries — and fails — to blame the state’s homelessness epidemic on someone, anyone else.

items.title: The Biden Diagnosis
items.description: We wish the former president well, but there is nothing untoward or scurrilous about the citizenry asking who knew what — and when.

items.title: Who Is the President Here?
items.description: On Russia and beyond, the VP seems to be signaling policy preferences that do not comport with those of the administration he serves.

items.title: The World Health Organization Is Excluding Taiwan — at China’s Behest
items.description: It is time for the WHO to take a more pragmatic and inclusive approach — one that puts public health above politics.
